        Features
        --------
        
        Support CIDR-like notation:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            >>> from port_range import PortRange
            >>> pr = PortRange('1027/15')
            >>> pr.port_from
            1027
            >>> pr.port_to
            1028
            >>> pr.bounds
            (1027, 1028)
        
        Parse and normalize port ranges:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            >>> pr = PortRange(' 4242-42 ')
            >>> pr.bounds
            (42, 4242)
            >>> str(pr)
            '42-4242'
        
        Access to decimal-representation properties:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            >>> pr = PortRange('1027/15')
            >>> pr.base
            1027
            >>> pr.prefix
            15
            >>> pr.mask
            1
            >>> pr.offset
            3
        
        
